# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# uuid.UUID.__dict__ dunder name length ordering
#
# Wave 352 theme: name lengths for novel dunders __init__, __new__ (absent), __repr__.
#
# '__eq__'(6) < '__str__'(7) < '__new__'(7) < '__init__'(8) == '__repr__'(8) == '__hash__'(8)
# '__new__'(7) == '__str__'(7): both 7-char dunder names.
# '__init__'(8) == '__repr__'(8) == '__hash__'(8): all 8-char dunder names.
# No prior uuid spec anchors the dunder name length including __init__ and __repr__.
# Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

